  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Monte Sarago is on a hillside next to Ostuni. And from up here, the views across to the old town are stunning. Head straight to the Attico Rooftop 225 terrace, order a drink or some delicious local food and enjoy the views. There's a small spa with a sauna and a Turkish bath which is a great place to re-charge your batteries before exploring some more of <a data-udi="umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0c28188245b40a396dd64fb346dffcd}" title="Puglia">Puglia</a>. You can walk to the centre of Ostuni in around 15 minutes and the coastline is just a short drive away.</p>
<p>Inside, the hotel is bright and modern with spacious rooms. If you want to make the most of the location, upgrade to a superior panoramic view room - they offer maximum comfort and great views that you can enjoy from your own furnished terrace. </p>
<p>Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Hotel Monte Sarago is approx. 50 mins from Bari or Brindisi airport.</p>]]></description>
