  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>are spacious and decorated in a light tones, giving them a fresh feel. They have twin or double beds, TV, minibar, air conditioning, safe, free Wi-Fi and a hairdryer. They can sleep up to two people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are bright and modern with plenty of space. They sleep up to three people.</p>
<p><strong>Panoramic View Rooms</strong> sleep up to two people and have superb views over Ostuni. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Panoramic View Rooms </strong>are around 32m² and have panoramic views from the furnished terrace. They have the same facilities as standard rooms and sleep up to two people.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms for Sole Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
